*Five players have been able to score more than one hat trick: [[Jaime Lazcano]], [[Santiago Bernabéu Yeste|Santiago Bernabéu]], [[Paulino Alcántara]], [[Lionel Messi]] and [[Ferenc Puskás]] have all scored two hat-tricks in El Clásico history ('''2''').

